(1, 'DNB', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><u>What mean to be an Academic Health Centre</u></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Thirty-two years back, when government medical colleges were the only institution to pursue medical education, Choithram Hospital and Research Centre came up with the idea to establish an academic health care centre first of its kind in Central India where teaching, research and health care are combined to provide the best possible clinical care that uses cutting edge technologies, resources and therapies that other community hospital may not have.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">With the idea that Academic success is pivotal for a successful career and growth, Choithram Hospital and Research Centre started DNB courses in 1990 that provide Post Graduate Degree courses. To date, our hospital has accreditation for 11 DNB courses.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><u>DNB Diplomat of National Board of Examination</u></strong>&nbsp;–</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The National Board of examination is a government of India establishment that aims to improve the quality of Medical Education by establishing high &amp; uniform standards of postgraduate study in modern medicine.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The nomenclature of the qualification awarded by the national board of examination is “Diplomate of National Board” (DNB).</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><u>Academic Departments</u></strong>&nbsp;–</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Choithram Hospital is a centre for research-oriented basic and clinical departments representing the leading edge of medical sciences. Our academics and clinical teams are comprised of consultants from various disciplines who collaborate through research, interdisciplinary programme and comprehensive patient services to all the ten academic departments running Broad speciality super speciality and postgraduate DNB courses.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><u>Departments with Superspeciality DNB courses &nbsp;</u></strong></p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 20px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><li style=\"line-height: 26px;\">Critical Care Medicine</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px;\">Gastroenterology</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px;\">Neurology</li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><u>&nbsp;</u></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><u>Department with Broad Speciality DNB degree courses &nbsp;</u></strong></p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 20px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><li style=\"line-height: 26px;\">Anesthesiology</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px;\">ENT</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px;\">General Medicine</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px;\">General Surgery</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px;\">Obstetrics &amp; Gynecology</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px;\">Pediatrics</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px;\">Radio diagnosis</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px;\">Orthopedics – Accreditation till 2020</li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">To date, 448 Doctors have been registered for DNB courses in various disciplines. With 286 successful candidates and a more than 90 % of pass-out rate, Choithram Hospital produces excellent results through its highly experienced team &amp; program.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Academically successful doctors are more likely to be employed, have sustainable jobs, and hold important posts in various Government and Private institutions Nationally &amp; Internationally. Some have established good nursing homes as practising renowned clinical practitioners and service the society.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">After pursuing a Postgraduate DNB degree, many students have done or do Superspeciality or fellowship in various disciplines.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Undergraduate (BDS) dental students of Rau Dental College have been getting their training in medicine and surgery here since 2003, and Choithram Hospital is the examination centre for practical exams of BDS students in surgery and treatment.&nbsp;<b>Fellowships</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Post-MD/MS doctors have also opted for training in various sub-specialities, including Paediatrics, Cardiology, Surgery and Dialysis. Formal fellowships in Burns and National Neonatology Forum (NNF) and Indian Academy of Paediatrics (IAP) have been stated since 2004, and Fellowship in Pain Medicine from 2012 and Indian Academy of Pain&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Medicine (IAPM) from 2020. Doctors from various national and international places are coming for fellowship in the Burns, Pediatrics and Pain Medicine departments.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><u>Paramedical&nbsp; &nbsp;Courses</u></strong>&nbsp;–</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">CHRC has opened its doors for practical training in Microbiology, Biochemistry. Dietetics, Hospital Management, Laboratory Medicine, Physiotherapy, Biotechnology Dialysis, Ventilation, Imaging, and OT Technician are some required courses in various specialities that are in demand amongst the students of the city and outside from various places of MP. Overseas students have also opted for their training in different things here.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">DMLS courses affiliated with DAVV were running from 1991 to 2003, and 300 students passed. PhD students are enrolled in Microbiology and Biochemistry, and 15 students have done PhD in these subjects, respectively. The two-year post 10 + 2 DMLT program started in 2006, and more than 300 students have passed.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">CHRC has signed MOU with IIT, IIM, RRCAT, DAVV&amp; other academic and research institutions to exchange expertise &amp; skills.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><u>Research&nbsp;</u></strong><strong><u>–</u></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The seeds of research were sown in 1997 with the formation of an academic committee, but the actual scientific research committee was formed in 1998.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">As with the famous quote that necessity is the mother of invention, to meet the need for training and research, a separate Ethical Committee was formed &amp; registered with DGCI in 2002. More than 100 research projects, including multinational projects, have been reviewed and cleared.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><u>What are the benefits of going to an academic medical center</u></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">With Clinicians, nurses, researchers, and teachers working in unison, patients have access to the latest medical breakthroughs and training that provides better medical care to them.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">At Choithram Hospital, our team of experts are not only trained in using modern technologies, but they also develop them. Choithram Hospital remains committed to looking ahead at the future of medical care, which is why we focus on teaching the future generation of medical professionals the best ways to care for their patients.</p>', 1, '2022-12-23 11:25:35'),
(2, 'Dietetics', '<h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong>Brief Introduction-</strong></span></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The dietetics Department at Choithram hospital is the pioneer of the teaching-learning process in the field and is very well established.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Department has a significant value on International and National grounds in Dietetics and Nutrition.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">A big team of Dieticians with great experiences and good credentials is working at the hospital from the academic perspective, they are efficiently providing practical training to budding future dieticians, and more than thousands of dieticians have been training at our institution.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Academia holds firm ground as many academic programs are available at this department, including practical training, international fellowship programs, dissertation work, short-term training, regular internship, specialized training, RD Internship and so on.</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\">Academic Activities-</h2><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 20px; clear: both;\">Objective</h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The primary purpose is to provide the best training and prepare future dieticians with sound practical Knowledge.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Why Practical Internship and training are essential –</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Practical learning is the most vital part of this profession and is sometimes mandatory to complete their post-graduate curriculum.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Students of Nutrition and Dietetics science gain basic Knowledge by learning theoretical aspects during their college curriculum. These internship programs build their confidence in applying that Knowledge here with us. It’s based on the Knowledge to action.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The continuous process of academic activities held at the Department of Dietetics throughout the year includes regular CNE (Continuous Nutrition Education) Programs, Clinical nutrition case presentations by our RD Students and RD Trainers and fellow colleagues.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Courses-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">A wide range of training programs is available at the Dietetics department, and the below information will provide detailed descriptions of our programs.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(227, 8, 8);\">1).&nbsp; INTERNATIONAL BURNS NUTRITION FELLOWSHIP PROGRAM</span></strong></p><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 20px; clear: both;\">Short Description of courses</h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">It’s an international fellowship program available through Interburns (an International network of training education and research in burns) www.interburn.org.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">This fellowship program has been developed under the capacity building for burns professionals, and the aim is to train more burn team members for nutrition support services.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">This program is a unique training program as none of the institutions across the globe is conducting such a program. We began in 2014 and trained many country fellows through this fellowship program, including the UK, GHANA, Nepal, Malawi, and India. A total of 12 fellows have received training.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">https://interburns.org/news/nutrition-fellowship-indore</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The application process is through the Interburns website, and interested candidates can fill out and submit their application through email; the selection process is through Interburns core committee and a strong commitment from the applicant.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Who can apply- anyone who has a strong commitment towards the management of burn and specialized in any field of burns multidiscipline (Dietician, Nutritionist, Nurse, Doctor and therapist) can send their application throughout the year</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">https://interburns.org/training/#training-fellowships</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Duration- There is no fixed duration for this fellowship program, but we suggest at least one month to learn practical skills.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Course Includes-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">This program is based on the practical posting, ward rounds, case presentation, and a short research dissertation work in burns nutrition during this fellowship.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Program Lead-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Ms Pratibha Sharma(Profile Link)</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(227, 8, 8);\">2). REGISTERED DIETICIAN INTERNSHIP</span></strong></p><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 20px; clear: both;\">Brief description</h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Department of Dietetics, Choithram Hospital and Research Center is the only Madhya Pradesh institute with a maximum seat (6) for Registered Dietician Internships accredited by the RD board of the Indian Dietetic Association.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">http://idaindia.com/registration/hospitals-for-rd-training/</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">A registered Dietician Internship is a mandatory part of fulfilling the eligibility criteria to write the All India registration exam by IDA India. (It’s a competitive exam held annually).</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">http://idaindia.com/who-is-rd/</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Duration-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">It’s a six-month specific internship program based on the competency package by the RD board.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Seats- 6 seats</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Eligibility-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Postgraduate students of Nutrition and Dietetics with a valid degree from a UGC-recognized University in India.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Application and admission process-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Our department conducts a short entrance test based on the basic knowledge of nutrition and dietetic science, which an individual applicant needs to pass to get eligibility for admission to this Internship program.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">An application can be emailed to us at dietetics@choithram.org or personally submitted to the department with all attested degrees and mark sheets.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">RD Trainers –</p><ol style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 20px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><li>Mrs Poornima Bhale (HOD Dietetics Department, more than 30 years of professional experience)(Profile Link)</li><li>Mrs Vibhuti Trivedi (Profile Link)</li><li>Ms Pratibha Sharma (Profile Link)</li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(227, 8, 8);\">3). SHORT TERM DIETETIC INTERNSHIP</span></strong></p><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 20px; clear: both;\">Brief description</h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">This internship is meant to fulfil the degree requirement and provides an overview of practical application knowledge in nutrition and dietetics.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Duration-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">It takes a few weeks to a few months. (Depending upon the institutional and candidate’s requirement)</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Seats- UPTO 40</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Eligibility-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Undergraduate and postgraduate students of nutrition and dietetics.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Application and admission process-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">A reference letter from the institution and an application from the candidate are required to obtain admission to this program.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The important dates-any date is acceptable for this program.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><br>4). GENERAL INTERNSHIP<br>Brief description-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">This Internship program is meant to train more postgraduate dietetic students where they learn and enhance their practical skills in depth under the supervision of their senior dieticians.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Duration-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Minimum of three months to six months and can be upto a year.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Seats-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Upto 20.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Eligibility-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Candidates held a master’s degree and diploma in Nutrition and Dietetics from a recognized university.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Application and admission process-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Direct applications through email or in person, which includes their attested documents of degree and mark sheets and a statement of purpose to enrol for this program.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Important dates-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Throughout the year.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><br>5). DISSERTATION WORK-<br>Brief description-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Research is an essential part of best practices and learning, and many universities have a separate module for dissertation work at the graduate and postgraduate levels in Nutrition and Dietetics.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">We accept students from recognized universities who wish to fulfil their dissertation work under our clinical nutrition supervisors.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Duration-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">As per their university or institutional requirement</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Seats-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Not fixed</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Eligibility- UG and PG students of Nutrition and Dietetics</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Application and admission process-</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Send your completed application to&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:dietetics@choithram.org\" style=\"color: rgb(229, 243, 246); touch-action: manipulation; box-shadow: none; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s;\">dietetics@choithram.org</a></p>', 1, '2022-12-23 11:26:21');

