(5, 'Mission Vision And Values', '', '<h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><strong>Mission</strong></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Our mission is to provide quality and affordable healthcare to all segments of society with world-class diagnostic facilities, state-of-the-art equipment, and medical professionals of eminence within a safe &amp; ethical environment.</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><strong>Vision</strong></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">We aim to be the best super specialty tertiary care referral institute for providing quality, ethical &amp; affordable healthcare to all sections of society.</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><strong>Values</strong></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Choithram Hospital has its values imbibed in every member. The values are embedded in the logo name “CHRC.”</p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 20px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 26px;\">“C”: Compassionate, Comprehensive, Collaborative Care to all patients and community by competent health care personnel.</li><li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 26px;\">“H”: Holistic Care and Hospitality of the highest expected standard as per the need of patients and their relatives within available resources.</li><li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 26px;\">“R”: Respect for all patients and their relatives about their Rights and Responsibility, Values and Customs. Respect for all our employees about their Rights and Responsibilities, Growth, Training, and Development.</li><li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 26px;\">“C”: The cost of the world-class state-of-the-art facilities is affordable by all strata.</li></ul>', 'Mission-Vision-And-Values', 1, 'ce70aab2e38a8e73e609f565c24fd970.jpg'),
