(9, 'Endocrinology', '<h1 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 44px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both;\">Endocrinology Hospital in Indore</h1><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong>Overview</strong></span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">department of Endocrinology and Metabolism is well established at CHRC. All types of endocrine cases including obesity is treated with skill and care.</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong>Endocrinology And Metabolism</strong></span></h2><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\"><strong>Brief Outline of the Department’s functions/ services/ diseases/ treatment:</strong></h3><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Endocrinology is a super specialized branch of medicine that deals with the diagnosis and treatment of all hormone disorders like Diabetes (Type I, Type II, GDM), Thyroid disorders (Hypothyroid and Hyperthyroid), Growth disorder (Short stature/ Acromegaly)</li></ul><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong>Services</strong></span></h2><p style=