(14, 'Interventional Spine And Pain Centre', '<h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong>Overview</strong></span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">With state-of-the-art equipment and multidisciplinary specialists, CISPC is a one-stop, non-surgical solution for spine and pain management. CISPC’s motto is to alleviate and treat pain so as to improve the overall quality of life for its patients. Multidisciplinary team includes interventional spine &amp; pain specialist, neurosurgeon, neurologist, orthopaedic surgeon, physiotherapist, psychologist, neuro-psychiatrist &amp; dietician<br>The Centre uses Alpha Philips Cathlab machine capable of fluoroscopy, cine-loop, DSA (Digital Subtraction, Angiography) &amp; Road Map, 2nd generation Radiofrequency generator</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong>Services</strong></span></h2><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\"><strong>The Interventional Spine and Pain Centre offers the following services and medical procedures:</strong></h3><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Percutaneous Endoscopic Discectomy (PELD)/ Transforaminal Endoscopic Discectomy under local anaesthesia</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Facial pain/ trigeminal neuralgia rad