(17, 'Ophthalmology', '<h1 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 44px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both;\">Best Eye Hospital in Indore</h1><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong>Overview</strong></span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Choithram Netralaya, under the aegis of Choithram Group, is dedicated to providing world-class ophthalmological care for one and all. The Netralaya works tirelessly to provide unbiased, unaltered and humane eye care services. For more information about Choithram Netralaya please visit Choithram Netralaya’s</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><b>Best Eye Hospital in Indore – Choithram Hospital</b></p>', 0),
(18, 'Obstetrics And Gynaecology', '<h1 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 44px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both;\">Gynaecology Hospital in Indore</h1><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong>Overview</strong></span></h2><div style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Department of Obstetrics &amp; Gynaecology is a self-contained department with a separate OT, labour room and 50-bedded ward, with an obstetric ICU. A team of consultants who are luminaries in their field is present 24/7, ably supported by registrars and housemen.<span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong><br></strong></span></div><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong>Natural Child Birthing Centre</strong></span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Birth may be a matter of a moment but it is a unique one. By honoring &amp; embracing all the many possible variations that birth encompasses, we at ‘SWA’ help take the fear out of the birth …In this way, every birth is a natural birth: each of us is part of nature, not separate from it, and nature is always stunning in its variety. Your birth, then, is part of the natural world, however, it unfolds</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong>Services</strong></span></h2><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\"><strong>Department of Obstetrics &amp; Gynaecology offers the following services, facilities, and medical procedures Endoscopic Laparososcopy:</strong></h3><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Endoscopic Hysteroscopy</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Thermachoice Balloon therapy for DUB</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Colposcopy for early cancer detection</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">PAP Smear</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Uro-Gynaecology surgery</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Sonosalpingography</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Painless Labour</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Interventional Sonography</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Uterine Artery Emolization</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Fallopian tube re-canalization</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Special Clinics for High-risk pregnancy, Infertility, Adolescent, Family planning and Menopause</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">The antenatal unit is well equipped with modern gadgets for monitoring mother and fetus in the most effective manner.</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Labour room has been provided with Cardio-tocography machine, conventional and color Doppler sonography, transport incubator [to transfer the high risk and premature babies to nursery.</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">HSG, Hysteroscopy, diagnostic laparoscopy and USG guided invasive procedures<br>CHRC is the only hospital in central India having YAG LASER for laparoscopic surgery and CO2 LASER for cervical lesions.</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Thermachoice Uterine Balloon Therapy a minimally invasive technique, done on OPD basis in CHRC for menorrhagia patients.</li></ul><div style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><b>Best Gynaecology Hospital In Indore – Choithram Hospital&nbsp;</b></div>', 0),
(19, 'Orthopaedics', '<h1 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 44px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both;\">Orthopaedic Hospital in Indore</h1><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong>Overview</strong></span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">CHRC’s Department of Orthopaedics is one of the first dedicated orthopaedic centres in Central India. The Department of Orthopaedics offers many specialized services and procedures and is renowned across Central India.</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong>Services</strong></span></h2><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\"><strong>Advanced Arthroplasty Centre</strong></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The department has a state of the art Arthroplasty OR equipped with laminar airflow and body exhaust suits which reduce the risk of infections. All primary and revision joint replacements and resurfacing, including complex cases involving hip, knee, shoulder, and elbow are performed here. Annually over 400 arthroplasties are performed in the JRS (Joint replacement and Spine) Operation Theatre Complex which includes around 100 revision surgeries.</p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\"><strong>Comprehensive Spinal Care Center</strong></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The department is involved in treating all levels of spinal surgery ranging from routine lumbar degenerative disc disease to complex cervical spine and craniovertebral anomalies. Annually, over 500 spinal surgical procedures are performed in the JRS (Joint replacement and Spine) Operation Theatre Complex.</p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong>Arthroscopy &amp; Sports Surgery</strong></span></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The department is involved in treating a wide variety of sports-related injuries ranging from acute ligament/tendon tears to chronic overuse injuries.</p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\"><strong>Advanced Trauma Surgery</strong></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The CHRC hospital has comprehensive trauma services available through emergency medical services. A large number of primary and neglected extremities, pelvic and spinal trauma is treated in the emergency center. Trauma is also operated in a planned manner in the routine theatres. We are equipped with an image intensifier and good technical and instrumentation support in all the operating rooms. Plastic surgery and vascular surgery departments provide excellent supportive care for the severely injured limb where limb salvage may be necessary. A vascular intervention and angioembolisation facility is also available within the hospital premises</p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\">Limb Lengthening and Deformity Correction with Ilizarov Method</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The department has been at the forefront for many years in using the Ilizarov technique for limb reconstruction. Specialized services offered include management of infected non-unions, limb lengthening, complex deformity correction, management of bone defects resulting from trauma or tumour resection. Some of the pioneering work from the department has been in the field of non-unions, tumour reconstruction, deformity correction, amputation stump lengthening, and limb lengthening in short stature dwarfism.</p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\"><strong>Orthopaedic Oncology including Limb Salvage Surgery</strong></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The department treats over 200 cases of orthopaedic neoplasms annually. These include both benign and malignant bone tumours. All types of limb salvage surgery and tumour reconstructive surgery including resection Arthroplasty are performed. Patients requiring chemotherapy and radiotherapy are referred to Cancer Wing which is on the same campus.</p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\"><strong>Subspecialty Services</strong></h3><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">The department provides specialized procedures for Knee, Shoulder, Hip, Ankle, Elbow, and Spine.</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Knee</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Meniscectomy</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">ACL &amp; PCL reconstruction</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Synovectomy</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Multi-ligament reconstructions</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Patellar realignment procedure</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Mosaicplasty</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Autologous chondrocyte implants</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Shoulder</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Arthroscopic &amp; mini-open Bankart</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Congruent arc Latarjet for bone defects</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Rotator cuff repair</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Acromioplasty</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Synovectomy</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Hip</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Diagnostic Hip</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">arthroscopy</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Loose body removal</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Ankle</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-l