; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Laminectomy for Cervical and Lumbar Canal Stenosis</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Trauma Spine Management</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Vertebroplasty and kyphoplasty for Osteoporosis</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Spine Infection Management</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Spine deformity evaluation and management</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Non-fusion Spine Procedure</li><li style=\"line-height: 26px; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Interventional Pain Management</li></ul><div style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><b>Best Orthopaedic Hospital in Indore – Choithram Hospital&nbsp;</b></div>', 0),
(20, 'Nephrology', '<h1 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 44px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both;\">Nephrology Hospital in Indore</h1><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong>Overview</strong></span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The Department of Nephrology at CHRC caters to the complete range of kidney disorders and is one of the most renowned centers in the state of Madhya Pradesh.</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong>Services</strong></span></h2><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\"><strong>The Department has following artificial Kidney Units:</strong></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Haemo Dialysis (HD): currently equipped with 27 stations for Haemo-dialysis units catering for routine IPD/OPD patients as well as emergency patients.<br>2. Peritoneal Dialysis (PD): Routinely acute and chronic PD (CAPD) services are available round the clock. Qualified and experienced doctors team available round the clock for placement of permanent peritoneal catheters.<br>Intensive care renal replacement Therapy for patients with multiple organ dysfunction syndromes such as Resistant Congestive Cardiac Failure, Hepatic Failure Multi and organ dysfunction (MODS) is carried on specialized machines in the Intensive care unit.</p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\"><strong>Renal Transplantation</strong></h3><div style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><div><div>CHRC is one of the premier institutes in India to have started the Living Donor Kidney Transplant (LDKT) surgery since 1985. It has always maintained high ethical standards by carrying out Transplantation on related Donors as per the guidelines laid by the “Human Organ Transplant Act – HOTA”. CHRC is also recognized for Cadaver Kidney Transplant. More than 850 transplant procedures as having been successfully carried out at CHRC.</div><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\"><strong>Renal dietary services</strong></h3></div><div style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;Specialized renal dietary advice is available through qualified consultants for IPD as well as OPD patients</div><div style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Best Nephrology Hospital in Indore – Choithram Hospital</div></div>', 0);
