-align-content); gap: var(--gap); flex-basis: var(--flex-basis); -webkit-box-flex: var(--flex-grow); flex-grow: var(--flex-grow); flex-shrink: var(--flex-shrink); -webkit-box-ordinal-group: var(--order); order: var(--order); align-self: var(--align-self); position: relative; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight ); width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\" style=\"transition: background 0.3s ease 0s, border 0.3s ease 0s, border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s;\"><div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Insititute of Cancer Sciences, Choithram Hospital &amp; Research Centre has grown to become one of the best centers for cancer care in Central India in 12 years, Insititute of Cancer Sciences caters to more than 10,000 cancer patients every year from all over MP and Chhattisgarh and Maharashtra.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Our goal is to take the fight against cancer to the next highest possible level and set new clinical benchmarks.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">While there are many treatment options available for cancer treatment, which could be through Surgery or through chemotherapy, Radiation therapy plays an important role in treatment of most cancers. Nowadays, using the latest radiation machines, one can allow for delivery of maximum radiation doses to the tumour with minimum spillage to normal organs in the vicinity of the tumour with highest degree of precision.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">We are Equipped with the latest Synergy LINAC machine, the Department of Radiation Oncology offers excellent care to cancer patients. With a sophisticated conformal beam-shaping technology and High Dose-rate mode delivery, this machine is designed to provide precision &amp; speed necessary to deliver advanced Intensity Modulated Radiation Therapy (IMRT),Volumetric Modulated Arc Therapy (VMAT)&nbsp; and Image Guided Radiation Therapy (IGRT) techniques that demand the maximum accuracy in tumor targeting while protecting the other surrounding tissues &amp; critical structures. We excel in treating cancer and take pride to be one of the best cancer institutes in Central India.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">We were the first centre in Central India to start Intensity Modulated Radiation Therapy and Image Guided Brachytherapy in 2009. Till now we have treated more than 6000 cases of different sites.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Our technological excellence reflects in:</p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; font-weight: 400; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Elekta Synergy Triple Energy Digital Linear accelerator</li><li style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; font-weight: 400; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Monaco TPS with Monte Carlo dose calculation algorithm most accurate available algorithm till now in hospital.</li><li style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; font-weight: 400; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">KV Cone beam CT (XVI),&nbsp; EPID</li><li style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; font-weight: 400; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">IBEAM EVO &nbsp;couch with 3 degrees of freedom</li><li style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; font-weight: 400; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Radiation oncology Information System- MOSAIQ system</li><li style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; font-weight: 400; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Image Guided Radiation Therapy (IGRT)</li><li style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; font-weight: 400; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Volumetric Modulated Arc Therapy (VMAT)</li><li style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; font-weight: 400; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Intensity Modulated Radiation Therapy (IMRT)</li><li style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; font-weight: 400; list-style: disc; margin-left: 10px !important;\">Three&nbsp; Dimensional&nbsp; Conformal therapy (3DCRT)</li></ul></div></div></div></h2><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: normal; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><strong><u>Precision Radiotherapy:</u></strong></h2><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: normal; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6c879aa elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6c879aa\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\" style=\"--flex-direction: initial; --flex-wrap: initial; --justify-content: initial; --align-items: initial; --align-content: initial; --gap: initial; --flex-basis: initial; --flex-grow: initial; --flex-shrink: initial; --order: initial; --align-self: initial; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-box-direction: normal; flex-direction: var(--flex-direction); flex-wrap: var(--flex-wrap); -webkit-box-pack: var(--justify-content); justify-content: var(--justify-content); -webkit-box-align: var(--align-items); align-items: var(--align-items); align-content: var(--align-content); gap: var(--gap); flex-basis: var(--flex-basis); -webkit-box-flex: var(--flex-grow); flex-grow: var(--flex-grow); flex-shrink: var(--flex-shrink); -webkit-box-ordin