gy</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"\">Professional Summary</font></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Dr.Suruchi Singh has completed her M.B.B.S from S.S. Medical&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">College and Gandhi Memorial Hospital, Rewa (M.P.)&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">and M.D. in Radiotherapy from&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">M.G.M. Medical College and Government Cancer Hospital, Indore</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;in 2004</span><br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">She has a Post M.D. Experiences include:</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">&nbsp;1. Working as Senior Registrar in Tata Memorial Hospital, Mumbai</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">2. Working as Independent Consultant Clinical Oncologist at Priyamvada Birla Cancer Research Institute, Satna, M.P.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">3. Working as Consultant Radiation Oncologist at Bhagwan Mahaveer Cancer Institute, Jaipur, Rajasthan.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">4. Working as Consultant Radiation Oncologist at CHL- CBCC Cancer Hospital, Indore.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">5. Working as Consultant Clinical Oncologist at IIHNO, Rau, Indore.</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: RGB (209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\">Technical Skills</span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">1. Interstitial implant and mold brachytherapy procedures at various sites with image guidance.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\"><b>2.&nbsp;</b>Expertise in&nbsp;<b>Conventional 2-D &amp; Clinical Planning, 3-D Conformal Planning,&nbsp;</b><b>PET and MRI-based Planning, IMRT, Virtual Simulation, and 3-D Brachytherapy planning.</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">3. Expertise in high precision&nbsp;<b>Radiotherapy techniques viz. IMRT, IGRT, VMAT</b>.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">4.&nbsp;<b>Special expertise</b>&nbsp;in&nbsp;<b>IMRT and 3-D conformal planning in Head &amp; Neck, Breast, and Gynecological malignancies.</b></p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"\">Scientific and Medical Societies Membership</font></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">i. ASSOCIATION OF RADIATION ONCOLOGISTS OF INDIA.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">II. INDIAN MEDICAL ASSOCIATION.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">III. INDIAN ASSOCIATION OF PALLIATIVE CARE.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">IV. ASSOCIATION OF SURGEONS OF INDIA.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">V. INDIAN SOCIETY OF ONCOLOGY.</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"\">Publications</font></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">i. Techniques of tumor bed boost irradiation in breast-conserving therapy: current evidence and suggested guidelines.– Acta Oncol. 2007;46(7):879-92.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">ii. Leptomeninges as a site of relapse in locally controlled diffuse pontine glioma with a review of literature – Child’s Nervous System: 2007;23(1):117-121.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">iii. Retrospective Analysis of Carcinoma Vulva cases in the last 10 years.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">iv. Head And Neck Mucosal Melanomas: The TMH experience – International Journal of Head Neck Surgery, VOLUME&nbsp;<strong>1</strong>&nbsp; ISSUE&nbsp;<strong>3, 2010.</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">v. Eyelid tumors: Retrospective analysis of the last 10 years.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">vi. Hypo fractionated radiotherapy for palliative whole brain radiotherapy: a new regimen. A Prospective Study.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">vii. Compliance with hormonal therapy in patients with breast cancer: A prospective study.</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\">&nbsp;</h2><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"\">Conferences and Seminars</font></h2></div></div></div><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-87959bb elementor-widget elementor-widget-image-carousel e-widget-swiper\" data-id=\"87959bb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;slides_to_show&quot;:&quot;3&quot;,&quot;slides_to_scroll&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;navigation&quot;:&quot;none&quot;,&quot;autoplay_speed&quot;:2000,&quot;speed&quot;:200,&quot;autoplay&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;pause_on_hover&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;pause_on_interaction&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;infinite&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;image_spacing_custom&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:20,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]}}\" data-widget_type=\"image-carousel.default\" style=\"--flex-direction: initial; --flex-wrap: initial; --justify-content: initial; --align-items: initial; --align-content: initial; --gap: initial; --flex-basis: initial; --flex-grow: initial; --flex-shrink: initial; --order: initial; --align-self: initial; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-box-direction: normal; flex-direction: var(--flex-direction); flex-wrap: var(--flex-wrap); -webkit-box-pack: var(--justify-content); justify-content: var(--justify-content); -webkit-box-align: var(--align-items); align-items: var(--align-items); align-content: var(--align-content); gap: var(--