(1, 'Admission Process', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">CHRC Casualty / Emergency Room is well equipped with state-of-the-art modern technology and the latest instruments of the medical field, along with senior nursing staff and well Skilled critical care Doctors.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Patient Arrives in Casualty (From OPD / Outside)</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; |&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;Initial Assessment Done in 3 mins.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;|&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><ol style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 20px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><li>If the MLC case Patient Attender Sent to CMO for MLC&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>Other Patients Registration.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Other Patients&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 20px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 26px;\">After Primary Evaluation Patient is given initial treatment.</li><li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 26px;\">The concerned Consultant Informed and called Casualty.</li><li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 26px;\">For Admission, Attenders sent to the CMO counter &amp; Admitted Accordingly From the Admission counter.</li><li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 26px;\">Patient Admitted &amp; IPD not Generated, Patient shifted to particular Dept { Ward / Pvt/ Gen/ Icu/ OT /etc.}.</li></ul>', 1, '2022-12-23 08:43:51'),
(2, 'International Patients', '<h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 20px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>International Patients</strong></span></h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">–Welcome to Choithram Hospital &amp; Research center-Indore (Madhya Pradesh), India</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Choithram Hospital &amp; Research Centre has focused on quality healthcare with a healing touch since its inception, and it’s been continuously working towards it. CH&amp;RC is NABH accredited and has also got Nursing&nbsp;Excellence Certification. Choithram Hospital &amp; Research Centre is a 350 bedded multi/super specialty hospital with a glorious record of serving the International patient and National community from Central India and abroad for Four Decades.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Choithram Hospital &amp; Research Centre is spread over 40 acres of Land in a lush green environment with 75 specialists and Super specialists as in-house consultants, who are available round the clock to deal with any emergency to ensure the best quality service to the patient community.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">There is a team of 60 junior doctors to look at patients’ health. The Hospital has employed all qualified nursing staff to provide the best nursing care. Our Hospital’s Department of Laboratory only Pvt. The Hospital in India’s 60 bedded Pediatric ward has a certified level III NICU &amp; PICU with 35 beds &amp; specialized facilities for transporting sick babies from referral hospitals.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Since its inception in 1979, Choithram Hospital and Research Centre has been perpetually involved in the best patient care services with a healing touch at par with International standards.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">We have established many Super specialties for the first time in central India, the First Cardiac Surgery, the first renal Transplant center, the first liver Transplant centre, the First Nuclear Medicine Centre, First state of the art Triple Energy Linear Accelerator Elekta Synergy with the facility of VMAT, IGRT, IMRT for Cancer Patients, First advanced Department of GI Sciences, World’s acclaimed burn Surgery Centre &amp; now announces most comprehensives well-developed state of art Interventional Spine &amp; Pain Centre, Only dedicated center for the first time for the management of chronic Pain.</p><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 20px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>WHAT WE STAND FOR</strong></span></h4><ol style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 20px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><li><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 20px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Clinical Excellence</span></h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Delivering the best of clinical care with healing touch is our sacred responsibility to each of our patients; thus, it is a way of life at Choithram Hospital and Research Center.</p><ol style=\"padding-left: 20px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li aria-level=\"1\">Technological Advancements</li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Modern technology plays a vital role in every aspect of our lives, and we at Choithram Hospital and Research Center seek to harness this technology to improve healthcare.</p><ol style=\"padding-left: 20px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li aria-level=\"1\">Pioneering Treatments</li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Working the extra mile, there is no competition and going in the direction, no one has to find a cure for our patients is fundamental to the functioning of Choithram Hospital and Research Center.</p><ol style=\"padding-left: 20px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li aria-level=\"1\">Dedicated Staff</li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">The staff at Choithram Hospital and Research Center is highly trained and ingrained in delivering the best clinical intervention and remaining steadfast in their duties.</p><ol style=\"padding-left: 20px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li aria-level=\"1\">Patient Experience</li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Delivering a delightful patient experience is at the heart of our efforts. We strive for patients and caregivers to leave our premises happy and satisfied.</p><ol style=\"padding-left: 20px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li aria-level=\"1\">Transparency and Ethics</li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">We are completely transparent with our patients to avoid any uncomfortable surprises. Upholding the highest standards of medical ethics is our priority.</p></li></ol><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 20px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">OUR CREDIBILITY</span></h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">42 Years of Clinical Excellence</span></strong></p><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 20px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Delivering advanced treatments and care for the most challenging cases.</span></h4><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 20px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">350 Bed Capacity</span></h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">One of Central India’s largest healthcare brands.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">1350 Transplant Surgeries Undertaken</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">We are offering new hope and life to patients in highly critical situations.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">10000 IPD &amp; 80000 OPD Patients Treated Annually</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">By a dedicated team of doctors, nurses and allied medical professionals.</p><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 20px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">194 International Patients Treated</span></h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>MOST FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</strong></span></p><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 20px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What kind of assistance do Choithtram Hospital and Research centre offer overseas patients?</span></h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Choithram Hospital and Research Center offer end-to-end patient care services for international patients visiting Choithram Hospital and Research Center facilities in India. Right from establishing contact with the hospital, one of our dedicated staff members will remain in touch with you. They will help secure appointments and visas, assist with travel arrangements, and stay in India.</p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Do Choithtram Hospital and Research centre receive and treat a</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;lot of overseas patients?</span></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Yes, Choithram Hospital and Research Center receive many overseas patients yearly to seek advanced medical treatment for various disorders. Our primary international patients come from the Middle East, Africa, and South Asia.</p><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 20px; clear: both;\">&nbsp;</h4><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Does Choithram Hospital and Research centre conduct any special clinics for overseas patients?</span></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Yes,&nbsp;<b>Choithram Hospital and Research Center conduct</b>&nbsp;Tele consultations for International patients.</p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\"><b>What other ways of connecting with doctors at Choithram Hospital and Research centre?</b></h3><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 20px; clear: both;\"><b>Choithram Hospital and Research Center allow patients to get in touch with their doctors via telemedicine and video conferences. Patients can send in their queries and reports via email and seek a video consultation.</b></h4><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 20px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">EXPERIENCE WORLD-CLASS HEALTHCARE AT CHOITHRAM HOSPITAL &amp; RESEARCH CENTER</span></h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Everything at Choithram Hospitals and Research Center offers you the best patient experience, including the most advanced treatments, state-of-the-art infrastructure and taking care of the simple things that make a big difference. Our effort isn’t just towards successfully overcoming an ailment. It is to help you become and remain healthy.</p><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 20px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">OUR SPECIALITIES</span></h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-seri