=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); touch-action: manipulation; box-shadow: none; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s;\"><strong>Rheumatology</strong></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gleneaglesglobalhospitals.com/spinal-surgery-hospital\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); touch-action: manipulation; box-shadow: none; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s;\"><strong>Spinal Surgery</strong></a></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><a href=\"https://www.gleneaglesglobalhospitals.com/surgical-gastroentrology-hospital\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); touch-action: manipulation; box-shadow: none; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s;\"><strong>Surgical Gastroenterology</strong></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gleneaglesglobalhospitals.com/surgical-oncology-hospital\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); touch-action: manipulation; box-shadow: none; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s;\"><strong>Surgical Oncology</strong></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gleneaglesglobalhospitals.com/transfusion-medicine-hospital\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); touch-action: manipulation; box-shadow: none; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s;\"><strong>Transfusion Medicine</strong></a></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><a href=\"https://www.gleneaglesglobalhospitals.com/urology-hospital\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); touch-action: manipulation; box-shadow: none; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s;\"><strong>Urology</strong></a></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><a href=\"https://www.gleneaglesglobalhospitals.com/vascular-endovascular-surgery-hospital\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); touch-action: manipulation; box-shadow: none; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s;\"><strong>Vascular &amp; Endovascular Surgery</strong></a></span></p><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 20px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Advanced Care</span></h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Choithram Hospital and Research Centre offers comprehensive consultation and care at its Outpatient Department expert doctors. Excellent diagnostic facilities, state-of-the-art consultation infrastructure and dedicated staff provide patients with a sensitive, understanding and advanced OPD clinic. Patients can book appointments via the online booking engine on the website or contact us via our helpline numbers. Unless it is an emergency, we encourage patients to seek an appointment and arrive at the appointed hour. This allows us to serve you hassle-free, providing you with the best value for the time you spend with us.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">For your first visit, please bring along with yourself</p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 20px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 26px;\">Any previous medical records, diagnostic reports and any other relevant</li><li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 26px;\">A caregiver, preferably a close family member or</li><li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 26px;\">An open mind &amp; willingness to pursue treatment to regain your</li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">At Choithram Hospital and Research Center, you, the patient and your caregivers must be at the heart of all your health-related decisions. We are facilitators and advisors and will work with you tirelessly to restore your health. We endeavour to see you in the pink of your health at the earliest with the least possible inconvenience caused to your daily routine.</p><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 20px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We are committed to deliver an exceptional Patient Experience</span></h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Delivering an exceptional patient experience is deeply ingrained into our processes and personnel. Our commitment to personalized care matches our excellent medical expertise. At Choithram Hospital and Research Center, we are steadfastly committed to bringing hope, wellness and assistance to patients and caregivers. We believe in strengthening lives through compassionate care, innovative therapies and relentless efforts.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>It’s your health, Stay Informed, Stay healthy………..</strong></span></p>', 1, '2022-12-23 09:15:26'),
(3, 'Facilities in OPD', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The Outpatient Services at Choithram Hospital and Research Centre cover all the central clinical departments for consultation with specialist doctors daily between 9:00 A.M. to 1.00 P.M at nominal registration charges as applicable for documentation. Specialist doctors are also available from 1 P.M.to 8 P.M for regular paid consultation as per the schedule. All new patients must register at the registration counter on arrival for consultation and deposit registration fees as applicable.</span><br></p>', 1, '2022-12-23 09:16:19'),
(4, 'Corparate Patients', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">An Empanelled Corporation is an organization that has enrolled with Choithram Hospital and Research Centre to provide medical services for its employees. Below is the list of Empanelled corporations and organizations.</p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\">We provide services to patients from:</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;1 – Airport Authority of India<br>&nbsp;2 – Avtec Motors<br>&nbsp;3 – Bank Note Press, Dewas<br>&nbsp;4 – Bank of Baroda<br>&nbsp;5 – Bharat Sanchar Nigam Limited (BSNL)<br>&nbsp;6 – Bridgestone India Private Limited<br>&nbsp;7 – CIL Textiles P. Limited<br>&nbsp;8 – Craftsman Automation Private Limited<br>&nbsp;9 – Cristopia / Khems Engineering Private<br>&nbsp;10 – Crompton Greaves<br>&nbsp;11 – Directorate of Soybean Research<br>&nbsp;12 – Gas Authority of India Limited<br>&nbsp;13 – Glenmark Generics<br>&nbsp;14 – Indian Institute of Management<br>&nbsp;15 – Indian Institute of Technology – Indore<br>&nbsp;16 – Indian Oil Corporation Limited<br>&nbsp;17 – Innovative Clad-Solutions Private Limited<br>&nbsp;18 – Larsen &amp; Toubro (L&amp;T)<br>&nbsp;19 – Lupin Limited<br>&nbsp;20 – Mahindra Two Wheelers<br>&nbsp;21 – Man Industries<br>&nbsp;22 – Narmada Hydraulic Development Corporation<br>&nbsp;23 – National Thermal Powers Corporation (NTPC)<br>&nbsp;24 – Oriental Bank of Commerce<br>&nbsp;25 – Raj Ratan Global Wire<br>&nbsp;26 – Raja Ramanna Centre for Advanced Technology<br>&nbsp;27 – Ranbaxy Laboratories Limited<br>&nbsp;28 – Spentex Industries Limited<br>&nbsp;29 – State Bank of India<br>&nbsp;30 – State Govt. Employees<br>&nbsp;31 – Steel Authority of India Limited<br>&nbsp;32