width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">Providing preauthorization&nbsp; form to the patient attandant&nbsp; and requests them to fill&nbsp; basic details&amp; Signed properly &amp; later mediclaim co-cordinator contacts the treating consultant to fill &amp; sign it.</font></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 0pt;\"><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">3.</font></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">&nbsp; Collect patient ID’s &amp; Policy detail</font></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">Mediclaim Co-ordinator &nbsp; collects customer ID card (ex. Aadhar Card)/ Pan Card etc.) With Insurance Card copies &amp; policy paper of last 3 years.</font></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 0pt;\"><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">4.</font></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">Login/Initiate for Initial Approval</font></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">Mediclaim Co-ordinator will send all the necessary documents to Insurance company / TPA for initial approval and Change the Inpatient category of the patient as cashless and add the name of concerning company in HIMS, and after initial approval&nbsp; He/She update the approval amount in same IPD in HIMS</font></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 0pt;\"><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">5.</font></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">Enhancement process</font></span></p><font face=\"Verdana\"><br></font></td><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">Initial approval is very meager and if bill of the patient is on higher side, then enhancement process is Initiated by mediclaim co-ordinator.</font></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 0pt;\"><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">6.</font></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">Initialization for Final Approval/ Discharge process</font></span></p><font face=\"Verdana\"><br></font></td><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">The entire original&nbsp; documents i.e. Discharge summary, Final Bill, Medical bills, Investigation reports etc. is to be sent to the concerning&nbsp; TPA/Insurance company for the final approval.</font></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 0pt;\"><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">7.</font></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">Settlement of mediclaim patient bills&nbsp;</font></span></p><font face=\"Verdana\"><br></font></td><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">After receiving final approval of the mediclaim patient, Entries done in settlement register which is sent to the billing department to collect difference amount. Then no-dues sent to concern ward to release the patient from hospital.</font></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 0pt;\"><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">8.</font></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">Uploading, Online file Submission</font></span></p><font face=\"Verdana\"><br></font></td><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">All the original documents attached and filled properly by billing department along with the covering letter of Assistant director – Health services are to be sent online via using particular portals.</font></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 0pt;\"><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">9.</font></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">Physical File Dispatching</font></span></p><font face=\"Verdana\"><br></font></td><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">After submission online, physical files are necessary to sent to the concerning mediclaim companies for settlement of claim.</font></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 0pt;\"><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">10.</font></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">Settlements of Claims</font></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">All the settlements are thoroughly checked and verified by Mediclaim Coordinator and receipt are generated against the settlement then it sent to accounts department to settle the patient bill accordingly.</font></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><br></p>', 1, '2023-03-01 09:02:39'),
(6, 'Our Campus', '<h1 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 44px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both;\"><strong>Our Campus</strong></h1><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 22px; clear: both;\"><strong>Our Services</strong></h3><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><strong>Nursing Services:-</strong></h2><h1 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 44px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;\">Nursing Service is one of the largest divisions of Choithram Hospital and Research Centre that employs over 300 nursing personnel. It comprises the Inpatient &amp; Outpatient Units, Operating Rooms, Critical Care Units and Peripheral units of the Hospital.&nbsp;</p></h1><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><strong>Emergency Services:-</strong></h2><h1 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 44px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;\">Our Emergency Services division specializes in the acute care of patients who present themselves without a prior appointment. Due to the unplanned nature of patient attendance, the department must provide initial treatment for a broad spectrum of illnesses and injuries, some of which may be life-threatening and require immediate attention. It requires different equipment and different approaches than most other hospital divisions. Patients frequently arrive with unstable conditions, so they must be treated quickly.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;\">Choithram Hospital and Research Centre have four ambulances, 24hrs medical shop, and dressing and observation rooms to cater to Emergency cases.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;\">Choithram Hospital and Research Centre’s emergency services are equipped to:&nbsp;</p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 20px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;\"><li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 26px;\">Provide first aid and emergency medicine in cases such as accidents, burn points, etc</li><li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 26px;\">Save lives by providing effective treatment 24/7&nbsp;</li><li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 26px;\">Receive all patients irrespective of age, caste, sex, religion or status&nbsp;</li><li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 26px;\">Admit the patient to the suitable ward as per the condition of the patient</li></ul></h1><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><strong>Out-Patient Services:-</strong></h2><h1 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 44px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;\">The Outpatient Services at Choithram Hospital and Research Centre cover all the central clinical departments for consultation with specialist doctors daily between 9:00 A.M. to 1.00 P.M at nominal registration charges as applicable for documentation. Specialist doctors are also available from 1 P.M.to 8 P.M for regular paid consultation as per the schedule. All new patients must register at the registration counter on arrival for consultation and deposit registration fees as applicable.</p></h1><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><strong>In-Patient Services:-</strong></h2><h1 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 44px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;\">Choithram Hospital &amp; Research Centre’s Inpatient services cater to all the registered patients with the medical departments 24/7. &nbsp;CHRC has 350 beds, which are divided into General, Semiprivate, Private, Deluxe, Super Deluxe Wards, and Special suites. All the wards and rooms are&nbsp;equipped with state of the art medical furniture and equipment. &nbsp;We have 8 operation theatres that work round the clock.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;\">We provide the following support services:</p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 20px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;\"><li style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Blood Bank</p></li><li style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">24X7 Pharmacy</p></li><li style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Waiting Lounge</p></li><li style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Prayer Hall</p></li><li style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">24 hours&nbsp;Clinical Laboratory and Pathological Services</p></li><li style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Specialized Dialysis Services</p></li><li style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Regional translator Services</p></li></ul></h1><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><strong>Intensive Care Services:-</strong></h2><h1 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 44px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;\">The Intensive Care Unit at CHRC is a 21 bedded tertiary care ICU with four isolation beds and an additional eight-bed dedicated ICU for cardiac patients. The ICU is ventilated and well-lit, with a reliable central air conditioning unit. It is a state-of-the-art ICU equipped with Ventilators – invasive and non-invasive, Multipara monitors – with both invasive and non-invasive modulation of monitoring, Bedside endoscopic and other GI procedures and dialysis, Defibrillators, ABG machines, ECG machines, IABP machine, Temporary pacemakers, DVT pumps, Nebulizers, ICU dialysis machine, Bedside X-Ray machine and Bedside USG with the echo machine.&nbsp;</p></h1><h2 style=\"margin-top: 19px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 15px; color: rgb(209, 37, 34); font-size: 19px; clear: both;\"><strong>Support Services:-</strong></h2><h1 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 44px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;\">W